Package com.ilm.projecto_ilm_backend.dto.project

Class ProjectProfilePageDto

java.lang.Object
com.ilm.projecto_ilm_backend.dto.project.ProjectProfilePageDto
public class ProjectProfilePageDto extends Object
Data Transfer Object for the profile page of a project. This class encapsulates comprehensive details about a project for display on its profile page, including metadata, state, members, and associated skills.

      members - List of project members.

      skills - Skills required for the project.
      statesToChange - Possible next states of the project.
      progress - Current progress of the project.
      maxMembers - Maximum number of members allowed in the project.
      typeOfUser - Type of user associated with the project.
      typeOfUserSeingProject - Type of user viewing the project.
      reason - Reason for the current state or action.
